{"title":"SQL Project Tutorial","html":"<h1 id=\"sql-project-tutorial\">SQL Project Tutorial</h1>\n<p>Step-by-step SQL project walkthrough.</p>\n<h2 id=\"project-employee-database-analysis\">Project: Employee Database Analysis</h2>\n<h3 id=\"step-1-create-database\">Step 1: Create Database</h3>\n<pre class=\"shiki dark-plus\" style=\"background-color:#1E1E1E;color:#D4D4D4\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">CREATE</span><span style=\"color:#569CD6\"> DATABASE</span><span style=\"color:#DCDCAA\"> company_db</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">USE</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> company_db;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"step-2-create-tables\">Step 2: Create Tables</h3>\n<pre class=\"shiki dark-plus\" style=\"background-color:#1E1E1E;color:#D4D4D4\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">CREATE</span><span style=\"color:#569CD6\"> TABLE</span><span style=\"color:#DCDCAA\"> departments</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> (</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">    department_id </span><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">INT</span><span style=\"color:#569CD6\"> PRIMARY KEY</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">    department_name </span><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">VARCHAR</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">(</span><span style=\"color:#B5CEA8\">50</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">);</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">CREATE</span><span style=\"color:#569CD6\"> TABLE</span><span style=\"color:#DCDCAA\"> employees</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> (</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">    employee_id </span><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">INT</span><span style=\"color:#569CD6\"> PRIMARY KEY</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">    first_name </span><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">VARCHAR</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">(</span><span style=\"color:#B5CEA8\">50</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">),</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">    last_name </span><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">VARCHAR</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">(</span><span style=\"color:#B5CEA8\">50</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">),</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">    salary </span><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">DECIMAL</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">(</span><span style=\"color:#B5CEA8\">10</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">,</span><span style=\"color:#B5CEA8\">2</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">),</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">    department_id </span><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">INT</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">    FOREIGN KEY</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> (department_id) </span><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">REFERENCES</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> departments(department_id)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">);</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"step-3-analyze-data\">Step 3: Analyze Data</h3>\n<pre class=\"shiki dark-plus\" style=\"background-color:#1E1E1E;color:#D4D4D4\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#6A9955\">-- Average salary by department</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">SELECT</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> d.department_name, </span><span style=\"color:#DCDCAA\">AVG</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">(e.salary) </span><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">AS</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> avg_salary</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">FROM</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> employees e</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">JOIN</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> departments d </span><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">ON</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> e.department_id = d.department_id</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">GROUP BY</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> d.department_name;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span></code></pre>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Congratulations!</strong> You've completed a SQL project!</p>\n","source":"19-sql-database-fundamentals/sql-database-project-tutorial.md","githubUrl":"https://github.com/NabidAlam/road-to-machine-learning/blob/main/19-sql-database-fundamentals/sql-database-project-tutorial.md","module":"19-sql-database-fundamentals","lessonId":"sql-database-project-tutorial","guideId":null,"type":"module"}